									<div class="description author withsidebar">
										<h6><a href="https://lithub.com/author/janelle-brown/">Janelle Brown</a></h6>
										Janelle Brown is a novelist, essayist and a journalist, and has written for <em>Vogue, The New York Times, Elle, Wired, Self, the Los Angeles Times, Salon</em>, and numerous other publications. She lives in Los Angeles with her husband and their two children.																			</div>
